msgstr ""

#: src/Onboarding/views/features.php:64
msgid "Tells search engines not to pass your site's ranking authority to the destination. Essential for affiliate, sponsored, or user-generated links so Google doesn't treat them as editorial endorsements — leaving affiliate links \"followed\" can trigger manual penalties. You can still override this per-link for trusted partners."
