#: src/Onboarding/views/features.php:98
msgid "Pretty Links counts your clicks, but MonsterInsights shows what visitors do next — which pages they read, how long they stay, whether they convert. Together you get both sides of the funnel: which links pull traffic in, and what that traffic actually does on your site."
